{"tid":227643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傅振中擺街站講「六四真相」：學生持槍傷公安 天安門冇屠殺","createTime":"2017-05-03T10:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T20:13:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb75e132e55cfd3e6373bf05937f80ee2c1cc6b","tid":227643,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170430/large/1493545417_008b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170430%2Flarge%2F1493545417_008b.jpg&h=d94f5ed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為紀念六四事件28周年，支聯會在石峽尾賽馬會藝術中心和社會文化發展中心合辦六四紀念館專題展，名為「六四關我？事」，讓市民思考六四與自身的關係；保衛香港運動、匯賢起動等團體組成「六四真相關注組」在銅鑼灣擺放街站，批評支聯會誇張失實。<br />\n<br />\n團體高叫「六四暴亂要睇清」、「軍警學生同遭殃」等口號，保衛香港運動主席傅振中批評，支聯會過去的說法誇張失實，又稱網上流傳的照片或短片，顯示當年部分學生及民運人士持槍或刀到場，用暴力傷害公安或解放軍，並非如支聯會所指的「手無寸鐵」。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170430/56634473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170430%2F56634473&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft25WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8eb9b215\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170430%2F56634473&h=4eca4082\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170430/56634473</a>"},{"pid":"49ae808a99328e51135287002a974fb73b73cbf1","tid":227643,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"唔爭在話埋文革無死人，<br />\n只係支共同大家開個玩笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23aad205d392e6ec13e27c5813b6648f377f4bff","tid":227643,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:46:24.000Z","msg":"係咪曲線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fcf01ded8b2aaad6e6af9014b4e64f31746b81","tid":227643,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c